<br>
Think of it this way. If your neighborhood were all devout catholics and you attented worship and cermonies with them, they would assume you to have the same beliefs as them.<br>
Now, if you decided you had some different ideas about catholic religion, that would most likely be ok with your friends, but once you started doing things that were extremely against the religion (like comitting genocide on other races), all of your neighbors would hang you from the highest tree!<br>
<br>
Get what I mean?<br>
<br>
<br>
